    "The accurate estimation of IRT parameters and the student state enhances the interpretability of the model in educational applications, allowing for appropriate learning interventions based on student ability and subjective difficulty.",
    "Additionally, the SAD-IRT model has the potential to predict dropout behaviors, providing valuable insights for preventing dropouts in online learning settings.",
